main module¶

This file contains functions necessary to open the main GUI window. This includes the main function that starts the main window.

main.main()[source]

Main function to run GUI

main.tex2png(output_folder='tex', tex_filename='var2tex.yml', overwrite=False)[source]

Create PNG for quantity(s) in TeX form. File containing quantity name(s) to TeX math format must be made before call.

Parameters

  • output_folder¶ – name of folder to save images in

  • tex_filename¶ – name of file containing name-to-TeX conversions. Keys in file are name of quantity. Values are corresponding TeX format.

  • overwrite¶ – set True to overwrite existing quantity if name already exists. Set False to skip quantities previously saved as TeX image.

Return type

None
